{"ID":270187, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"187\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs186.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs188.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 187<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">We are glad to hear of the organization of the different quorums in this city, and hope that their\n  organization will be attended to in every stake and branch of the Church, for the Almighty is a lover\n  of order<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> and good government.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">From the faith and enterprise of the Saints generally, we feel greatly encouraged and cheerfully\n  attend to the important duties devolving upon us,<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> knowing that we not only have the approval of\n  Heaven, but also that our efforts for the establishment of Zion and the spread of truth, are cheerfully\n  seconded by the thousands of Israel.<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">In conclusion we would say, brethren, be faithful, let your love and moderation be known unto\n  all men;<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> be patient, be mindful<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> to observe all the commandments<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> of your Heavenly Father, and\n  the God of all grace<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> shall bless you. Even so. Amen.<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span>&mdash;DHC 4:336-339.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"signatureBlock\">\n    <p class=\"signatureLine\">JOSEPH SMITH, President<\/p>\n    <p class=\"signatureLine\">ROBERT B. THOMPSON, Clerk.<\/p>\n  <\/div>\n  <p class=\"wideEllipse\">* * *<\/p>\n\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Prophet&rsquo;s Discourse on Gospel Principles<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">At 10 o&rsquo;clock a.m. [May 16, 1841], a large concourse of the Saints assembled on the meeting\n  ground, and were addressed by President Joseph Smith, who spoke at considerable length.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Doctrine of Agency<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">He commenced his observations by remarking that the kindness of our Heavenly Father called\n  for our heartfelt gratitude. He then observed that Satan was generally blamed for the evils which we\n  did, but if he was the cause of all our wickedness, men could not be condemned. The devil could not\n  compel mankind to do evil; all was voluntary.<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> Those who resisted the Spirit of God,<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> would be\n  liable to be led into temptation,<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> and then the association of heaven would be withdrawn<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> from\n  those who refused to be made<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> partakers of such great glory.<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> God would not exert any compulsory\n  means,<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> and the devil could not; and such ideas as were entertained [on these subjects] by many\n  were absurd. The creature was made subject to vanity, not willingly, but Christ subjected the same\n  in hope<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span>&mdash;all are subjected to vanity while they travel through the crooked paths<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span> and difficulties\n  which surrounded them. Where is the man that is free from vanity?<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span> None ever were perfect but\n  Jesus;<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116342\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116342)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116342)\">D&amp;C 132:8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114121\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114121)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114121)\">D&amp;C 59:15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115907\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115907)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115907)\">D&amp;C 123:17<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106241\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106241)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106241)\">Num. 10:4,36<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109877\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109877)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109877)\">Philip. 4:5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110560\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110560)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110560)\">2 Pet. 3:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106307\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106307)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106307)\">Deut. 15:5<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111573\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111573)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111573)\">Mosiah 4:30<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113774\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113774)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113774)\">D&amp;C 42:78<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110480\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110480)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110480)\">1 Pet. 5:10<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110676\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110676)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110676)\">Rev. 1:7<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113592\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113592)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113592)\">D&amp;C 33:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116745\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116745)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116745)\">Moses 1:42<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107296\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107296)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107296)\">Isa. 66:4<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112512\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112512)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112512)\">Hel. 14:31<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112100\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112100)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112100)\">Alma 30:46<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112114\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112114)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112114)\">Alma 32:28<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112641\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112641)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112641)\">3 Ne. 18:25<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111517\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111517)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111517)\">Mosiah 2:36<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112167\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112167)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112167)\">Alma 34:35<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112431\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112431)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112431)\">Hel. 4:24<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112495\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112495)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112495)\">Hel. 13:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115821\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115821)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115821)\">D&amp;C 121:37<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116319\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116319)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116319)\">D&amp;C 132:4<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110471\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110471)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110471)\">1 Pet. 5:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115022\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115022)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115022)\">D&amp;C 93:22<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115204\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115204)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115204)\">D&amp;C 101:35<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115849\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115849)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115849)\">D&amp;C 121:46<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109303\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109303)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109303)\">Rom. 8:20<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107267\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107267)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107267)\">Isa. 59:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111834\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111834)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111834)\">Alma 7:20<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113100\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113100)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113100)\">D&amp;C 3:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106803\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106803)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106803)\">Ps. 94:11<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106978\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106978)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106978)\">Eccl. 1:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107850\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107850)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107850)\">Matt. 5:48<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109903\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109903)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109903)\">Col. 1:28<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110340\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110340)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110340)\">Heb. 13:21<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110481\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110481)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110481)\">1 Pet. 5:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112620\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112620)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112620)\">3 Ne. 12:48<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114461\"><a href=\